combine in small food processor
 * 1 chopped onion 
 * 2 chopped garlic clove
 * 2 tbsp fish sauce 
 * 1/2 tsp white pepper
 * 1 tbsp lemongrass paste
process to a paste
combine with 
 * 600 g lean or extra lean ground pork
combine with 
 * 1/2 cup bread crumbs
form into 12 meatballs 
flatten lightly
cook on grill or in pan
option: glaze with
 * hoisin sauce

serve with salad or rice
option: form 4 burger patties 

Vietnamese noodle salad
combine for dressing 
 * 3 tbsp sugar 
 * 3 tbsp fish sauce 
 * 2 tbsp rice wine vinegar 
 * 2 tbsp lime juice 
 * 85 ml water
 * 3 minced garlic cloves 

cook
 * 400 g rice vermicelli

split into 4 bowls 

add
 * bean sprouts
 * chopped lettuce 
 * julienned carrots
 * julienned daikons or radishes
 * chopped coriander and/or mint
 top with dressing 


